preference.name: TC_overwrite_protection
preference.preference_description: This preference is used to indicate that the same property of the object has been modified concurrently by another user. A message will be displayed that will inform the user to discard their edits and update the property with latest value. When the preference is FALSE, the property value will be saved without any indication about concurrent modification. This will overwrite the property values modified by another user. Default value of this preference is FALSE. Applicable to Properties dialog, Form dialog, Viewer view, Summary view, Properties view and Details View inside My Teamcenter, BOM Window view within System Engineering, Office Live and Requirements applications.
